{"title":"赃物展览（图片）","authors":["池北偶","华君武"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":1,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"赃物展览"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗　华君武画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据华盛顿的美国艺术陈列馆最近宣布，今年春夏两季将在美国各地展览盗窃我国的古文物。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强盗亮赃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千古奇观。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青铜鼎、翡翠盘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古书、字画、珍珠衫……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"件件俱是无价宝，得来全凭偷、抢、占。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜光杯盛威士忌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛仔裤跨白玉鞍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秦筝伴奏阿飞舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此“风雅”，不堪看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赃物可称琳琅满目，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只还缺一件"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——中国的宝岛台湾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罪证齐全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他日好把账算！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}